				<div class="book-name">The Second Book of Machabees </div>
				<div class="act-chapter">
					<div class="prev-chapter"></div>|
					<div class="chapter">Chapter 1</div>
					|<div class="next-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220524160839/http://catholicbible.online/knox/OT/2_Mac/7899">next &gt;</a></div>
